<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٨٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3902">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4822">عَمْرٍو </a>: سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرًا </a>يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«الَّذِي قَتَلَ خُبَيْبًا هُوَ أَبُو سِرْوَعَةَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>